k=BBC Sport |date=8 August 2004 |accessdate=7 June 2019}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA Champions League]] runner-up: [[2005\u201306 UEFA Champions League|2005\u201306]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/4773353.stm |title=Barcelona 2\u20131 Arsenal |work=BBC Sport |date=17 May 2006 |accessdate=7 June 2019}}</ref>\n\n'''Germany'''\n*[[FIFA World Cup]] runner-up: [[2002 FIFA World Cup|2002]]; third place: [[2006 FIFA World Cup|2006]]\n*[[UEFA European Championship]] runner-up: [[UEFA Euro 2008|2008]]\n*[[FIFA Confederations Cup]] third place: [[2005 FIFA Confederations Cup|2005]]\n\n'''Individual'''\n<!--LEAGUE AND FEDERATION-SANCTIONED AWARDS ONLY. No fan or magazine-voted awards. Listed in chronological order from last time won.-->\n*''[[Kicker (sports magazine)|kicker]]'' [[Bundesliga]] Team of the Season: 1995\u201396<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/bl50/199596/startseite.html |title=Bundesliga Historie 1995/96 |language=German |publisher=kicker}}</ref>\n*[[Best European Goalkeeper|UEFA Goalkeeper of the Year]]: 1997, 2006\n*[[UEFA Club Football Awards]] Best Goalkeeper: 2005\u201306\n*[[2006 FIFA World Cup#All star team|FIFA World Cup All-Star Team]]: 2006\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{Soccerbase}}\n* [http://www.sporting-heroes.net/football/arsenal-fc/jens-lehmann-7456/league-appearances-for-the-gooners_a16134/ Profile] at sporting-heroes.net\n* {{Fussballdaten}}\n* {{WorldFootball.net}}\n* {{IMDb name}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Germany squads\n| bg = white\n| fg = black\n| bordercolor = black\n| list1 = \n{{Germany squad 1998 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Germany squad 1999 FIFA Confederations Cup}}\n{{Germany squad UEFA Euro 2000}}\n{{Germany squad 2002 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Germany squad UEFA Euro 2004}}\n{{Germany Squad 2005 FIFA Confederations Cup}}\n{{Germany squad 2006 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Germany squad UEFA Euro 2008}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Awards\n| bg = gold\n| fg = navy\n| list1 = \n{{2006 FIFA World Cup Team of the Tournament}}\n{{Best European Goalkeeper}}\n{{UEFA Club Football Awards}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lehmann, Jens}}\n[[Category:1969 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Essen]]\n[[Category:Footballers from North Rhine-Westphalia]]\n[[Category:German footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers]]\n[[Category:FC Schalke 04 players]]\n[[Category:A.C. Milan players]]\n[[Category:Borussia Dortmund players]]\n[[Category:Arsenal F.C. players]]\n[[Category:VfB Stuttgart players]]\n[[Category:2. Bundesliga players]]\n[[Category:Bundesliga players]]\n[[Category:Serie A players]]\n[[Category:Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers who have scored]]\n[[Category:UEFA Cup winning players]]\n[[Category:Germany under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Germany international footballers]]\n[[Category:1998 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:1999 FIFA Confederations Cup players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2000 players]]\n[[Category:2002 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2004 players]]\n[[Category:2005 FIFA Confederations Cup players]]\n[[Category:2006 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2008 players]]\n[[Category:German expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:German expatriate sportspeople in Italy]]\n[[Category:German expatriate sportspeople in England]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Italy]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in England]]\n[[Category:Arsenal F.C. non-playing staff]]\n[[Category:FC Augsburg non-playing staff]]\n[[Category:German male film actors]]\n", "name_user": "BundesBerti", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jens_Lehmann"}
